WEBVTT

00:07.031 --> 00:08.920
(Zhaowen Bookstore)

00:08.921 --> 00:11.661
you'll need at least a month to recover.

00:13.651 --> 00:14.871
I can't afford to wait anymore.

00:15.331 --> 00:16.871
The guard's life is hanging by a thread,

00:17.611 --> 00:19.541
and my mother's just passed away.

00:21.011 --> 00:22.591
What I need the most

00:23.171 --> 00:24.541
is not to heal,

00:25.201 --> 00:26.791
but to be able to hold my weapon.

00:30.361 --> 00:32.311
I knew it.

00:33.611 --> 00:35.311
I have medicine prepared for you.

00:36.081 --> 00:38.191
Take one when you are exhausted.

00:38.401 --> 00:39.981
You are draining your energy.

00:40.041 --> 00:42.341
Your strength
will be reduced by 30 percent.

00:43.251 --> 00:44.661
The bruises don't get to heal properly.

00:45.571 --> 00:47.701
Even if it's healed,

00:48.361 --> 00:50.101
you will experience pain for a lifetime.

00:50.721 --> 00:52.461
- If you trusted me...
- I trust you.

00:57.291 --> 00:58.431
The 70 percent of my strength

00:58.441 --> 00:59.741
is enough to fight against them.

01:09.311 --> 01:11.631
Just like the first half
of The Life of Luo Shan's story,

01:11.931 --> 01:15.261
it's hard to cut off your family
and to balance between it and loyalty.

01:15.721 --> 01:17.261
I'm not a watcher anymore.

01:17.721 --> 01:19.231
I'm part of the story now.

01:21.211 --> 01:22.351
I still remember

01:23.771 --> 01:26.151
the fox-faced woman once told me...

01:26.521 --> 01:27.791
If the second half of the story

01:27.881 --> 01:29.991
is about the son
interrogating his father,

01:30.771 --> 01:32.231
it'll be shocking.

01:32.521 --> 01:33.741
Do you think

01:33.931 --> 01:35.351
a son shouldn't interrogate the father

01:35.801 --> 01:38.181
and family is more important than
the truth?

01:39.051 --> 01:40.240
I mean,

01:40.241 --> 01:42.461
what's wrong with being shocking?

01:46.321 --> 01:48.381
We are not living in the play.

01:50.361 --> 01:53.431
It doesn't matter

01:53.961 --> 01:55.261
if you believed what happened;

01:56.241 --> 01:57.541
or if it's true.

02:20.761 --> 02:21.901
How could it be?

02:23.091 --> 02:24.231
Are you

02:25.291 --> 02:26.461
really not her?

02:29.411 --> 02:30.760
The most important thing now

02:30.761 --> 02:32.061
is to win the fight.

02:32.721 --> 02:35.271
Let's put the other things
aside for now.

02:36.601 --> 02:38.461
I'll get you some clothes.

02:43.531 --> 02:44.831
How did he escape?

02:45.291 --> 02:47.431
He was half dead.

02:49.041 --> 02:51.850
They have contact in the residence.

02:51.851 --> 02:53.711
They collaborated to save him.

02:53.761 --> 02:55.111
Send someone to get him!

02:55.121 --> 02:56.090
Search thoroughly in the Capital

02:56.091 --> 02:57.250
and get him back!

02:57.251 --> 02:58.391
- Yes, sir!
- Yes, sir!

02:59.131 --> 03:00.271
Hurry up.

03:00.691 --> 03:03.690
Interrogate Song Mo's guards!

03:03.691 --> 03:04.540
He was badly injured.

03:04.541 --> 03:06.741
I don't believe
he could get away from this.

03:07.041 --> 03:08.341
- Yes, sir.
- Also,

03:08.861 --> 03:10.290
get everyone from
the first and third family,

03:10.291 --> 03:11.130
and also the elders

03:11.131 --> 03:12.461
over here.

03:12.641 --> 03:13.920
I want to go into the ancestral hall.

03:13.921 --> 03:15.061
Yes, sir!

03:15.761 --> 03:16.901
Come back.

03:19.571 --> 03:21.061
All the men of sacrifices,

03:21.161 --> 03:22.431
have they all returned?

03:22.721 --> 03:24.151
Yes.

03:24.531 --> 03:25.671
Go.

03:26.671 --> 03:33.411
(Knocking Ice into Jade Chips)

03:34.601 --> 03:35.901
You've made your decision.

03:40.201 --> 03:41.341
You are right.

03:42.011 --> 03:43.431
No matter how shocking it is,

03:44.131 --> 03:45.901
we have to end the feud.

03:46.721 --> 03:47.991
Even if I die,

03:48.371 --> 03:50.391
even if everyone accused me of treason,

03:51.761 --> 03:53.941
as long as there is someone
who trusts and understands me,

03:55.371 --> 03:57.591
then this is a life
that's worthwhile for me.

03:58.201 --> 03:59.341
I promise.

03:59.761 --> 04:01.901
No matter what you do,

04:03.091 --> 04:04.621
or what the public says about you,

04:05.161 --> 04:06.391
I'll always support you.

04:08.011 --> 04:09.181
This is more than enough

04:10.531 --> 04:11.671
for me.

04:35.491 --> 04:36.631
(It's...)

04:43.491 --> 04:45.741
Fourth Young Lady,
you are the fox-faced woman.

04:45.761 --> 04:47.581
Why don't you tell His Lordship?

04:49.611 --> 04:50.871
Things aren't settled yet.

04:51.521 --> 04:54.431
I can't let other things affect him.

05:04.371 --> 05:05.911
I'll come back for you

05:07.571 --> 05:09.311
if I stay alive!

06:35.911 --> 06:40.110
=Blossom=
(Adapted from the novel "Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

06:40.111 --> 06:43.371
=Episode 13=

06:45.431 --> 06:48.811
(Funeral)

06:57.661 --> 06:59.860
Why is my heart beating so fast?

06:59.861 --> 07:01.270
- Stop it.
- Is this...

07:01.271 --> 07:07.851
(Duke of Ying's Residence)

08:10.761 --> 08:11.991
Where are my people?

08:17.271 --> 08:21.291
(Song Maochun,
Song family's Eldest Uncle)

08:23.571 --> 08:25.431
Entering the ancestral hall
in the middle of the night,

08:25.441 --> 08:26.440
(Song Fengchun)
we've been waiting

08:26.441 --> 08:27.551
(Song family's Third Uncle)
for four hours.

08:27.811 --> 08:29.501
I'm sure something is wrong.

08:29.961 --> 08:31.911
What could go wrong?

08:32.571 --> 08:34.730
He has been beaten over 100 times.

08:34.731 --> 08:37.431
Anyone else would be dead by now.

08:45.211 --> 08:46.351
Maochun.

08:56.111 --> 08:58.051
(Song's Ancestral Hall)

08:59.681 --> 09:01.461
My apologies.

09:01.851 --> 09:03.210
How dare you kill someone

09:03.211 --> 09:04.520
in the inner courtyard of
the Duke of Ying's Residence.

09:04.521 --> 09:05.911
This is an order from His Lordship.

09:05.971 --> 09:07.581
There are thieves in the house.

09:07.611 --> 09:10.311
We must separate
the family from the thieves.

09:10.491 --> 09:11.671
This will be the line.

09:11.771 --> 09:13.541
Anyone inside the ancestral hall
stays alive.

09:13.631 --> 09:15.511
Anyone outside the ancestral hall
will be killed.

09:19.611 --> 09:21.280
- Don't!
- How dare you!

09:21.281 --> 09:24.791
What do you think
the Duke of Ying's Residence is?

09:26.491 --> 09:28.330
We've never seen these people.

09:28.331 --> 09:30.031
Are they really thieves?

09:31.011 --> 09:34.031
Do you respect the law at all?

09:34.561 --> 09:37.221
This is outrageous!

09:51.451 --> 09:52.821
Lu Zheng!

09:55.091 --> 09:56.231
Lu Zheng.

09:57.491 --> 09:58.631
It's me.

09:59.041 --> 10:00.181
I'm back.

10:01.801 --> 10:02.971
Your Lordship,

10:04.011 --> 10:05.461
I didn't admit it.

10:06.401 --> 10:07.510
I...

10:07.511 --> 10:10.181
I didn't let you down.

10:13.401 --> 10:14.520
Brother!

10:14.521 --> 10:15.370
Go!

10:15.371 --> 10:17.520
Lu Ming, run!

10:17.521 --> 10:18.400
Brother!

10:18.401 --> 10:19.671
Get him out of the way!

10:20.011 --> 10:21.821
Take good care of His Lordship.

10:22.081 --> 10:23.221
Quick!

10:23.491 --> 10:24.631
Brother!

10:27.881 --> 10:30.221
Hurry up! Leave!

10:39.011 --> 10:40.221
Good job.

10:41.331 --> 10:42.581
You saved my life.

10:43.921 --> 10:45.391
They all saved my life.

10:45.611 --> 10:47.151
They…

10:47.451 --> 10:50.311
They wanted to force me
to put my thumbprint.

10:50.851 --> 10:51.991
I...

10:52.011 --> 10:54.941
I bit my fingers.

10:56.731 --> 10:59.101
So did the rest of us.

10:59.331 --> 11:00.981
None of us admit it.

11:05.041 --> 11:06.181
Lu Zheng.

11:06.561 --> 11:07.701
Stay with me.

11:08.041 --> 11:09.311
The medic is almost here.

11:09.801 --> 11:10.680
You can't die.

11:10.681 --> 11:11.800
Lu Zheng!

11:11.801 --> 11:13.061
Open your eyes!

11:16.091 --> 11:17.271
Your Lordship.

11:18.371 --> 11:19.701
Where is my brother?

11:23.161 --> 11:24.631
Brother, I'm here.

11:26.451 --> 11:27.591
Brother.

11:28.971 --> 11:31.671
Take care...

11:31.761 --> 11:35.821
Take care of His Lordship for me.

11:36.211 --> 11:37.351
I will.

11:37.611 --> 11:40.031
- Protect
- I will.

11:40.731 --> 11:42.941
His Lordship.

11:44.161 --> 11:46.271
Lu Zheng.

11:46.451 --> 11:47.591
Brother.

11:48.401 --> 11:49.671
Lu Zheng!

11:49.871 --> 11:51.311
Brother!

11:52.371 --> 11:54.341
Brother!

11:59.761 --> 12:00.901
Official Song!

12:16.751 --> 12:20.451
(Lofty Morality)

12:32.881 --> 12:33.720
Duke.

12:33.721 --> 12:34.640
They are here.

12:34.641 --> 12:36.701
We should run now.

12:37.251 --> 12:40.221
Well, well, well.

12:40.731 --> 12:43.391
He is Jiang Meisun's nephew indeed.

12:44.451 --> 12:48.311
His Lordship dares to push us
into such a situation.

12:49.401 --> 12:51.101
- I'm afraid he would...
- He wouldn't dare!

12:51.611 --> 12:52.751
And he couldn't.

12:52.971 --> 12:56.061
Li Zhen from Liaodong is approaching
the city with his soldiers,

12:56.211 --> 12:57.461
the disturbance is pressing,

12:57.641 --> 12:59.911
and His Majesty will not tolerate
internal rebellion.

13:06.731 --> 13:08.461
Take this sword.

13:09.761 --> 13:10.981
Go get help.

13:11.131 --> 13:12.010
I...

13:12.011 --> 13:13.151
Go!

13:15.681 --> 13:16.821
Yes, sir.

13:21.971 --> 13:23.111
Evil.

13:23.881 --> 13:26.671
I know what you're looking for.

13:30.451 --> 13:31.591
Han.

13:32.211 --> 13:33.160
Brother.

13:33.161 --> 13:34.301
Glad that you're fine.

13:35.681 --> 13:36.821
Brother.

13:36.881 --> 13:38.631
Can you don't be mad at father?

13:40.091 --> 13:41.231
I'm not mad.

13:42.451 --> 13:44.461
I'm killing those who are not loyal
to the family.

13:44.971 --> 13:46.341
Only when the family is at peace,

13:47.161 --> 13:48.911
then we can mourn our mother in peace.

13:51.561 --> 13:53.751
Where is the jade pendant
that Grandfather gave to you?

13:57.611 --> 13:59.101
I always bring it with me.

14:05.521 --> 14:07.221
I wasn't around when Mother was ill.

14:07.491 --> 14:08.701
Tell me about it.

14:10.041 --> 14:11.181
Where is Nanny Xie?

14:11.731 --> 14:13.221
She's been with Mother for decades.

14:14.371 --> 14:15.511
Where is she now?

14:16.131 --> 14:19.861
They said she was not well,
so they sent her home.

14:20.611 --> 14:22.151
But she ran into bandits
on the way back.

14:22.681 --> 14:23.821
She got killed.

14:27.011 --> 14:30.061
Which doctor did Mother go to?

14:30.451 --> 14:32.151
Her Majesty visited a few times.

14:32.521 --> 14:33.751
She was worried.

14:34.581 --> 14:36.981
Her Majesty recommended
the first doctor.

14:37.731 --> 14:39.751
Mother's condition worsened
during the fall season.

14:40.371 --> 14:43.181
His Highness recommended another doctor.

14:48.611 --> 14:49.490
Lu Ming.

14:49.491 --> 14:50.631
Yes.

14:51.041 --> 14:52.250
Guard the Xixiang Place.

14:52.251 --> 14:53.391
Yes.

14:53.761 --> 14:54.901
Brother.

14:57.131 --> 14:58.271
Please.

14:59.371 --> 15:00.581
Don't hurt father.

15:22.371 --> 15:23.701
- Brother.
- Brother.

15:24.131 --> 15:25.160
Come here.

15:25.161 --> 15:26.671
It's safe here.

15:44.681 --> 15:46.941
Father, is there anything
you would like to tell me?

15:58.491 --> 16:00.631
The Jiang family is now guilty.

16:01.371 --> 16:02.631
Uncle and I

16:03.331 --> 16:06.031
are considered guilty in your eyes too.

16:06.551 --> 16:08.671
Since you have the capability
to fight your way back,

16:09.281 --> 16:10.431
what do you want?

16:16.251 --> 16:17.981
I always see you as my father.

16:18.451 --> 16:21.821
Did you ever see me as your son?

16:22.161 --> 16:25.941
Silence is better than words.

16:26.041 --> 16:27.551
Adultery is a misunderstanding.

16:28.041 --> 16:29.861
Those who died are traitors.

16:30.401 --> 16:32.821
You can take your mother's dowry
and private property.

16:32.851 --> 16:34.151
We'll put everything

16:35.131 --> 16:36.461
behind us.

16:42.351 --> 16:44.271
Thank you for your words.

16:45.331 --> 16:48.431
I can now put our father-son bond

16:49.521 --> 16:51.061
behind too.

16:56.921 --> 16:59.311
During my last trip home,
you scolded me badly.

17:00.281 --> 17:01.791
I gave you this
as a token of reconciliation.

17:03.011 --> 17:04.791
I found it
in the utility room yesterday.

17:06.121 --> 17:09.271
The candle wick is white,
the outer layer is full of dust.

17:10.841 --> 17:13.191
You've never looked at it.

17:14.801 --> 17:15.941
All these years,

17:17.651 --> 17:19.581
it's me that is having
an extravagant hope.

17:20.121 --> 17:22.271
I took 40 strokes of the cane for you.

17:22.841 --> 17:24.551
And you punished me with a hundred flog.

17:24.731 --> 17:27.421
I've paid you back everything.

17:27.911 --> 17:29.901
From now on, we are no longer related,

17:30.731 --> 17:32.061
just like this lantern.

17:32.841 --> 17:33.860
The reason why

17:33.861 --> 17:35.791
I'm talking to you peacefully

17:35.801 --> 17:38.231
is for Mother's funeral.

17:38.361 --> 17:39.661
On my mother's First Seventh Ritual,

17:40.491 --> 17:41.631
I'll perform the rites.

17:42.801 --> 17:44.661
I'll hold the streamer

17:45.361 --> 17:46.661
during the funeral procession.

17:50.841 --> 17:52.951
You want to officiate the funeral

17:53.281 --> 17:55.581
to show everyone in the Capital

17:55.651 --> 17:57.650
that you are the Lordship.

17:57.651 --> 18:00.341
You are doing it for your benefit!

18:03.931 --> 18:05.410
Since I joined the army,

18:05.411 --> 18:08.191
I've never relied on this family.

18:08.321 --> 18:10.141
From now on, I'll rely on myself

18:11.211 --> 18:13.511
to get what I want.

18:14.281 --> 18:16.711
I'm moving to Grandfather's Yizhi Hall.

18:17.011 --> 18:19.381
From now on, we are not related.

18:21.081 --> 18:22.621
However, during the ceremony,

18:23.251 --> 18:26.341
you must fulfill your duty
as my mother's husband,

18:27.891 --> 18:29.791
so she can pass with honor.

19:08.171 --> 19:09.311
Su Lan.

19:09.561 --> 19:11.381
Burn the used gauze.

19:11.731 --> 19:13.141
Don't leave anything behind.

19:13.601 --> 19:14.751
Yes.

19:27.561 --> 19:28.901
An urgent letter from Lord Qing.

19:29.121 --> 19:32.421
(Harmony of Moral and Nourishing)
Li Zhen has been violating the border.

19:32.801 --> 19:35.311
People are deeply disturbed.

19:36.081 --> 19:37.381
In my humble opinion,

19:37.931 --> 19:41.490
Wang Xingyi should lead the Supreme
Commander of Military Affairs in Jiliao.

19:41.491 --> 19:42.901
Increase the troops by 30 thousand

19:43.251 --> 19:44.621
and fight with Li Zhen.

19:44.801 --> 19:46.751
Otherwise,
with the military strength in Liaodong,

19:47.121 --> 19:48.551
it would take only ten days

19:48.841 --> 19:51.661
for Li Zhen to invade Daitong.

19:54.211 --> 19:56.080
How's the treasury spending?

19:56.081 --> 19:58.141
Ministry of Construction is building
the Yuanyou Palace.

19:58.361 --> 20:00.341
We're not even halfway there yet.

20:06.601 --> 20:07.560
Your Majesty,

20:07.561 --> 20:09.600
The Li Zhen tribe is poor.

20:09.601 --> 20:11.560
We can tell from them urging us
to allow horse-trading

20:11.561 --> 20:12.760
in order to get food.

20:12.761 --> 20:13.900
They are starting a war

20:13.901 --> 20:15.650
just to loot food supplies

20:15.651 --> 20:17.751
and livestock for winter.

20:17.931 --> 20:20.321
We don't necessarily
need to engage in this.

20:20.771 --> 20:21.961
The Cabinet

20:22.241 --> 20:25.341
is discussing the military affair
with His Majesty,

20:25.491 --> 20:28.821
Lord Dou, don't use your knowledge
in the wrong place.

20:29.521 --> 20:30.390
Official Wu,

20:30.391 --> 20:32.061
this is a matter of national security.

20:32.211 --> 20:33.901
I dare not refuse to speak.

20:34.411 --> 20:37.170
If we can resolve the war in a month,

20:37.171 --> 20:39.001
the Ministry of Revenue
will be able to support it.

20:39.121 --> 20:41.581
However, if we can't resolve this
in three months,

20:41.691 --> 20:44.991
we'll have to raise taxes
to pay for military use.

20:45.081 --> 20:47.320
If that's so,
it'll affect the spring seeding of

20:47.321 --> 20:50.210
people in Su, Song, Jia, and Hu.

20:50.211 --> 20:51.080
Your Majesty,

20:51.081 --> 20:52.730
we shouldn't allow horse-trading.

20:52.731 --> 20:55.061
Previously, I was demoted
because of this.

20:55.121 --> 20:57.080
Now, I'm not afraid to do it again.

20:57.081 --> 20:59.730
Once we allow horse trading,
there will be corruption

20:59.731 --> 21:01.360
and breed criminals.

21:01.361 --> 21:02.840
Your Majesty,
please make a wise decision.

21:02.841 --> 21:04.170
Guard the country
and die for the people,

21:04.171 --> 21:06.330
this is the ancestral's motto.

21:06.331 --> 21:08.330
We are a righteous country.

21:08.331 --> 21:10.341
We will speak
even if it means death to us.

21:10.731 --> 21:12.791
We will speak
even if it means death to us.

21:15.651 --> 21:16.791
Your Majesty.

21:17.601 --> 21:19.341
Bring Her Majesty's elixir.

21:19.601 --> 21:20.741
- Yes, sir.
- Your Majesty.

21:30.651 --> 21:32.951
Only if Meisun is here.

21:36.571 --> 21:37.791
Did he send it in again today?

21:37.931 --> 21:39.191
Yes, Master.

21:39.301 --> 21:41.150
Ever since
the Fourth Young Lady was grounded,

21:41.151 --> 21:42.740
Mr. Wu has been sending a copy of

21:42.741 --> 21:44.610
Lessons for Women
through the back door every day.

21:44.611 --> 21:48.121
Occasionally, he would sneak in
some food and newspaper.

21:51.311 --> 21:54.381
His Oukai writing is angelic.

21:54.581 --> 21:56.231
(Lessons for Women)
That is good writing indeed.

22:01.611 --> 22:02.880
Has the Seventh Master departed?

22:02.881 --> 22:05.061
He departed after dinner.

22:05.121 --> 22:06.650
It'll take at least two weeks

22:06.651 --> 22:08.201
to audit the account
at the Taiyuan Residence.

22:09.761 --> 22:10.901
Master,

22:11.011 --> 22:13.061
last night,
regarding the Fourth Young Lady,

22:13.561 --> 22:14.701
what do you think?

22:19.121 --> 22:21.830
Dou Zhao is rebellious and arrogant.

22:21.831 --> 22:23.371
It's time to fix it.

22:24.361 --> 22:26.171
Send my word
to the Shengtian Prefecture.

22:34.071 --> 22:38.091
(Funeral)

22:45.511 --> 22:48.510
(Spirit Tablet of Jiang's Late Wife)

22:48.511 --> 22:52.371
(Longevity)

23:02.951 --> 23:06.091
(Funeral)

23:10.251 --> 23:12.010
The funeral is always officiated

23:12.011 --> 23:13.231
by the head of the family.

23:13.361 --> 23:14.821
Why is the eldest son

23:15.041 --> 23:17.360
taking over for the Duke?

23:17.361 --> 23:19.170
Song Mo hasn't shed a tear.

23:19.171 --> 23:20.381
Unfilial.

23:20.491 --> 23:21.631
You're right.

23:22.411 --> 23:24.210
What's wrong
with the eldest son taking over?

23:24.211 --> 23:25.250
Filial or not;

23:25.251 --> 23:26.210
Shed a tear or not,

23:26.211 --> 23:28.001
has nothing to do with you.

23:28.011 --> 23:29.930
They are from a family of officials
with meritorious records.

23:29.931 --> 23:31.421
The standard of funeral

23:31.601 --> 23:32.791
for Mrs Jiang is so shabby.

23:33.041 --> 23:34.010
Right.

23:34.011 --> 23:36.280
Lord Song is having
the time of his life.

23:36.281 --> 23:38.631
He hasn't even seen his mother
one last time.

23:40.281 --> 23:42.600
Watch your mouth.

23:42.601 --> 23:44.031
Stop being so mean.

23:44.801 --> 23:46.520
When he was fighting the pirates,

23:46.521 --> 23:47.490
where were you?

23:47.491 --> 23:49.621
I bet you didn't see your mother
one last time too.

23:53.041 --> 23:54.821
Gu Yu is here to pay respect.

23:57.601 --> 23:58.741
Don't worry.

23:58.891 --> 24:00.031
I'm with you.

24:00.221 --> 24:01.951
Next time, no one would dare
to speak ill of you

24:02.011 --> 24:03.951
on East Fourth Street.

24:07.411 --> 24:08.551
Thank you.

24:20.831 --> 24:24.211
(Lu Zheng, the Ding Army)

24:30.251 --> 24:31.391
Your Lordship.

24:31.871 --> 24:33.791
I, Lu Ming,
will take over my brother's place.

24:34.361 --> 24:35.661
From now on,

24:36.361 --> 24:37.951
I'll protect Your Lordship

24:39.011 --> 24:40.311
at all costs.

24:41.601 --> 24:43.991
We all know who killed Lu Zheng.

24:45.011 --> 24:46.151
But

24:47.891 --> 24:49.581
we can't avenge his death now.

24:51.251 --> 24:53.191
Will you still follow me?

24:57.321 --> 24:59.421
No matter Your Lordship's decision,

24:59.931 --> 25:02.061
I'm willing to be the vanguard.

25:02.361 --> 25:04.141
Please let me be part of your army.

25:08.081 --> 25:09.231
Bring me the wine.

25:17.081 --> 25:18.381
I, Song Yantang,

25:19.281 --> 25:20.951
will always remember your sacrifice.

25:23.211 --> 25:24.511
To my brothers.

25:25.361 --> 25:26.661
Rest in peace!

25:27.211 --> 25:29.061
Rest in peace!

25:39.071 --> 25:42.251
(Lu Zheng, the Ding Army)

25:46.801 --> 25:50.471
- Your Lordship!
- Your Lordship!

26:00.561 --> 26:02.421
How is it? Did anyone find out?

26:03.491 --> 26:04.631
Miss.

26:16.871 --> 26:19.010
(Lord Song
officiated Mrs Jiang's funeral)

26:19.011 --> 26:20.151
The situation is settled down.

26:20.211 --> 26:22.040
Song Mo officiated Mrs. Jiang's funeral.

26:22.041 --> 26:23.271
He was in charge of the funeral.

26:23.931 --> 26:25.471
The position is secured.

26:30.871 --> 26:33.531
(Unfortunately, Lu Zheng was killed.)

26:35.121 --> 26:36.581
Lu Zheng is dead.

26:38.691 --> 26:40.621
(Lu Zheng should be alive.)

26:40.911 --> 26:41.760
(But he's dead.)

26:41.761 --> 26:44.311
Ready for battle!

26:51.491 --> 26:52.631
Sister.

26:56.591 --> 26:57.450
Who is it?

26:57.451 --> 26:58.520
Fourth Young Lady,

26:58.521 --> 27:00.471
the Fifth Master wants you in
the ancestral hall.

27:15.491 --> 27:16.631
Fifth Uncle.

27:17.011 --> 27:19.141
Why do you want to see me at this hour?

27:20.321 --> 27:21.461
Ms. Longevity,

27:21.891 --> 27:23.970
you've been unhappy
with your marriage arrangement

27:23.971 --> 27:25.651
with the Duke of Jining.

27:25.761 --> 27:28.341
Tell us the truth.

27:28.691 --> 27:31.890
Perhaps, we can figure out some ways
to help you.

27:31.891 --> 27:33.061
What do you mean?

27:34.521 --> 27:35.600
Zou Er.

27:35.601 --> 27:36.741
Yes.

27:43.281 --> 27:44.280
The bloody garment, I...

27:44.281 --> 27:45.421
Su Lan!

27:45.561 --> 27:46.751
What is it?

27:47.731 --> 27:49.821
Seems like something is wrong
with the bloody garment.

27:49.891 --> 27:50.840
Fifth Brother.

27:50.841 --> 27:52.061
This is the proof.

27:52.891 --> 27:54.101
How is a bloody garment

27:54.691 --> 27:56.661
related to me?

27:58.361 --> 28:01.031
You are secretly meeting a man
outside of the family.

28:01.041 --> 28:02.901
You are a dishonor to the Dou family.

28:03.281 --> 28:04.421
Come in.

28:04.891 --> 28:07.471
The Fourth Young Lady has an affair
with an outsider.

28:07.601 --> 28:08.901
Bring out the family punishment.

28:09.521 --> 28:10.661
Yes, sir.

28:15.521 --> 28:16.410
Master.

28:16.411 --> 28:17.890
It's ready.

28:17.891 --> 28:19.711
Seventh Madam
asked you to make a decision.

28:21.081 --> 28:23.861
The elder will marry a man of honor,
the second will marry a man of power.

28:24.281 --> 28:25.621
It would have been perfect.

28:26.971 --> 28:28.511
However, the pawns disobey.

28:28.901 --> 28:31.071
We've come into a hopeless situation.

28:32.971 --> 28:34.711
Try to pass what's happening with
Dou Zhao

28:34.731 --> 28:36.381
to Wu Shan.

28:37.171 --> 28:39.061
If we can exchange him for it

28:39.931 --> 28:42.511
it'd still be worthwhile.

28:44.691 --> 28:46.751
Master, you mean...

28:48.651 --> 28:50.511
Didn't Wu Shan

28:51.321 --> 28:53.120
want to be with Dou Zhao?

28:53.121 --> 28:55.141
If he knew Dou Zhao was suffering,

28:57.121 --> 28:58.821
would he be anxious?

29:01.281 --> 29:03.101
Understood. I'll get it done.

29:25.451 --> 29:26.760
All thanks to the Duke's blessing.

29:26.761 --> 29:28.271
You've finally woken up.

29:28.931 --> 29:30.101
Lord Song regains consciousness.

29:33.361 --> 29:34.501
Lord Song!

29:35.281 --> 29:36.421
Lord Song.

29:36.521 --> 29:37.901
You're finally awake.

29:42.081 --> 29:43.341
How long have I been asleep?

29:44.651 --> 29:46.101
Seven days and seven nights.

29:47.041 --> 29:50.311
The imperial physician
has been here a few times.

29:51.081 --> 29:53.141
They say you've injured
your five viscera.

29:53.321 --> 29:55.231
You took the pills
that overthrew your body.

29:55.561 --> 29:56.951
You are exhausted

29:57.761 --> 29:59.551
and you might not wake up.

30:00.601 --> 30:03.661
Fortunately, you've survived this

30:06.011 --> 30:07.151
Where is Dou Zhao?

30:07.451 --> 30:08.751
How is she doing?

30:09.071 --> 30:10.791
- Fourth Young Lady...
- Lu Ming.

30:14.121 --> 30:15.261
What's wrong?

30:15.651 --> 30:16.791
Tell me.

30:18.651 --> 30:20.341
According to Mr. Chen,

30:21.011 --> 30:23.311
the Fourth Young Lady was punished
by Dou Fifth Master

30:24.121 --> 30:25.791
because she met with an outsider.

30:32.601 --> 30:33.951
Outsider.

30:34.651 --> 30:35.791
It's me.

30:38.971 --> 30:39.970
Lord... Lord Song.

30:39.971 --> 30:41.111
Lord Song.

30:41.681 --> 30:43.581
The family just went through
a devastating state.

30:44.281 --> 30:46.141
You merely escape from death.

30:46.281 --> 30:47.210
You can't take this.

30:47.211 --> 30:48.351
Yeah.

30:51.731 --> 30:52.901
She saved my life.

30:53.281 --> 30:54.511
If I can't make it,

30:54.631 --> 30:56.410
then let's take it as
I'm returning my life to her.

30:56.411 --> 30:57.840
In fact, the matter
with the Fourth Young Lady

30:57.841 --> 30:59.471
has already been settled.

30:59.561 --> 31:00.791
It's just the Wu family.

31:02.891 --> 31:04.031
Wu family?

31:04.411 --> 31:05.621
What's wrong with the Wu family?

31:09.251 --> 31:10.250
Sir, you can't go in.

31:10.251 --> 31:11.650
- Get out of my way.
- You can't go in.

31:11.651 --> 31:13.410
- Get out.
- What are you doing?

31:13.411 --> 31:14.621
Murder?

31:14.971 --> 31:16.111
Get out of my way.

31:17.281 --> 31:18.581
Fourth Young Lady.

31:29.411 --> 31:30.581
The bloody garment is mine.

31:31.491 --> 31:32.560
Mr. Wu,

31:32.561 --> 31:34.080
don't make a false confession.

31:34.081 --> 31:36.010
How could it belong to you?

31:36.011 --> 31:37.800
I was coughing up blood.

31:37.801 --> 31:39.621
As expected of the legal grandson
of the Wu's,

31:39.731 --> 31:41.141
a man of honor.

31:42.041 --> 31:43.341
But don't you think,

31:44.041 --> 31:45.730
it's a ridiculous reason?

31:45.731 --> 31:47.471
I was the one who acted boldly.

31:48.251 --> 31:50.141
I was the frivolous one.

31:50.211 --> 31:51.901
It has nothing to do
with the Fourth Young Lady.

31:52.361 --> 31:55.381
Minister Dou, please punish me.

31:56.171 --> 31:58.141
Official Wu bullies us
on the strength of his position,

31:58.331 --> 32:00.800
allowing his grandson
to break into the inner courtyard

32:00.801 --> 32:03.061
to seduce Dou's family's daughter
who is already engaged,

32:03.521 --> 32:05.581
treating us as if we were nothing.

32:05.731 --> 32:07.621
I'm not the one to make the call.

32:08.121 --> 32:10.311
Shengtian Prefecture
should make the call.

32:15.491 --> 32:17.791
Seducing a well-known family's daughter,

32:18.361 --> 32:20.661
you're going to be beheaded.

32:21.841 --> 32:23.471
Poor guy.

32:24.761 --> 32:25.901
That night,

32:26.651 --> 32:28.711
I was there to ask for medicine.

32:30.361 --> 32:32.381
We are innocent.

32:32.521 --> 32:34.490
You come from a family of scholars.

32:34.491 --> 32:36.511
How could you be innocent

32:36.691 --> 32:38.421
if you have been visiting
the Dou's Residence?

32:38.801 --> 32:40.141
There could be one reason.

32:40.491 --> 32:44.271
Official Wu wanted the ministers
to agree to start a war with Li Zhen.

32:44.651 --> 32:47.650
Did you go to Dou's Residence
to find out their view

32:47.651 --> 32:49.471
and to persuade them?

32:50.761 --> 32:53.381
What does this have to do
with my grandfather?

32:54.491 --> 32:56.511
In the time of danger and chaos,

32:56.891 --> 32:58.821
that's when you see loyalty in person.

32:59.211 --> 33:01.341
It's the duty of the servant

33:01.651 --> 33:03.551
to protect the country with his blood.

33:04.361 --> 33:06.511
Naturally,
we shouldn't tolerate traitors.

33:06.971 --> 33:09.791
There's no need to persuade.

33:11.651 --> 33:13.141
Wu Shan said

33:13.841 --> 33:17.560
that Official Wu thinks that now is
the time of danger and chaos,

33:17.561 --> 33:20.010
those who favor peace are not loyal.

33:20.011 --> 33:22.821
His Majesty tolerates traitors.

33:23.171 --> 33:26.450
Wu Shan went to Dou's residence
to seduce the daughter,

33:26.451 --> 33:28.760
intending to find out
Dou's officials' view,

33:28.761 --> 33:31.511
and planned to gang up.

33:31.561 --> 33:32.701
That's not true.

33:33.841 --> 33:35.341
You distort the truth.

33:35.411 --> 33:36.861
Who are you?

33:38.011 --> 33:39.151
Is anyone here?

33:39.601 --> 33:42.341
I want to meet Dou Shishu!

33:42.601 --> 33:44.280
Piles of water filled with blood

33:44.281 --> 33:46.341
were poured out of the Shengtian Prison.

33:46.561 --> 33:49.270
All the statement
is about Wu's family lobbying

33:49.271 --> 33:51.031
and trying to gang up.

33:51.521 --> 33:53.901
How about those civil servants
who are close to us?

33:56.001 --> 33:57.951
They returned all the money.

34:02.361 --> 34:03.751
I thought

34:05.171 --> 34:07.101
I saved his life.

34:08.491 --> 34:09.631
But now,

34:11.851 --> 34:13.631
I owe him my life.

34:19.721 --> 34:22.071
Dezhen has always been close
to the Dou family.

34:22.411 --> 34:23.901
I bet Lord Dou

34:24.451 --> 34:27.591
knows him very well.

34:28.451 --> 34:31.071
Please spare his life.

34:32.641 --> 34:35.631
Well, there's a line between public
and private interest.

34:35.991 --> 34:37.401
Xingyi, don't worry.

34:37.491 --> 34:39.721
Official Wu can also be assured.

34:39.731 --> 34:41.221
It's nothing big.

34:43.331 --> 34:44.770
Official Wu and I

34:44.771 --> 34:46.591
will remember your favour.

34:46.681 --> 34:48.631
On behalf of my student,

34:49.491 --> 34:50.631
thank you.

34:51.721 --> 34:52.861
Don't be.

34:55.091 --> 34:56.231
Take care.

35:06.831 --> 35:11.240
(Thorough Research and Deep Thinking)

35:11.241 --> 35:12.381
Fifth Uncle.

35:13.081 --> 35:16.541
I beg you to spare
Wu Shan and the Wu family.

35:17.561 --> 35:19.080
Zhao, go back.

35:19.081 --> 35:20.680
It's none of your business.

35:20.681 --> 35:22.861
Ever since Wu Shan
was in the Shengtian Prefecture,

35:23.731 --> 35:25.311
house servants of all civil servants

35:25.681 --> 35:28.141
have been coming to Dou's family.

35:29.081 --> 35:31.151
Lord Mu and Lord Zhao are here too.

35:31.421 --> 35:33.981
We receive countless letters every day.

35:34.251 --> 35:36.351
There is no way
they are letting it pass.

35:37.601 --> 35:39.901
It's not good for a woman
to be too smart.

35:40.051 --> 35:41.461
Having an affair

35:41.521 --> 35:43.581
is merely a scandal for other families.

35:43.821 --> 35:45.021
However,

35:45.081 --> 35:48.501
the Wu family
has been in power for decades.

35:49.201 --> 35:51.791
It's time to make way for other people.

35:52.291 --> 35:54.541
The day when
the prosperous Wu family falls,

35:57.081 --> 35:59.191
is the day you fulfill your ambition

35:59.811 --> 36:01.151
and makes a name.

36:01.371 --> 36:04.071
That's what you wanted
from the beginning, isn't it?

36:04.601 --> 36:06.341
A gentleman planned his time

36:06.521 --> 36:07.901
and acted when the time came.

36:08.411 --> 36:10.071
Going against God's will

36:10.201 --> 36:12.111
is not going to end well.

36:13.081 --> 36:14.221
Fifth Uncle,

36:18.521 --> 36:20.631
please!

36:21.491 --> 36:23.311
Spare Wu Shan!

36:31.791 --> 36:35.131
(Perpetual Bloom)

36:38.081 --> 36:39.221
Fourth Young Lady.

36:39.601 --> 36:41.370
We've got a reply from Mr. Chen.

36:41.371 --> 36:42.751
Lord Song has regained consciousness.

36:45.041 --> 36:46.381
It's good that he's awake.

36:47.491 --> 36:50.311
I heard that when Lord Song woke up

36:50.331 --> 36:51.821
and learned about the bloody garment,

36:52.621 --> 36:54.130
he wanted to go
to the Shengtian Prefecture

36:54.131 --> 36:55.330
to clear Mr. Wu's name.

36:55.331 --> 36:56.471
No!

36:57.411 --> 36:58.631
If he goes now,

36:58.721 --> 37:00.501
he'll end up the same as Wu Shan.

37:00.771 --> 37:02.861
Fifth Uncle, Song Yichun,

37:03.161 --> 37:05.311
or the mastermind
behind Duke of Ding's case,

37:05.331 --> 37:07.271
they all wanted both of them to be dead.

37:07.331 --> 37:09.151
Even Yan Chaoqing can't persuade him.

37:09.181 --> 37:10.671
And you were grounded.

37:14.371 --> 37:15.511
Ms. Longevity.

37:44.851 --> 37:45.991
Ms. Longevity.

37:46.811 --> 37:48.271
I'm late.

37:48.721 --> 37:50.180
I didn't expect so much would happen

37:50.181 --> 37:51.691
during my trip to Chanxi.

37:51.811 --> 37:53.541
I know you've suffered.

37:53.891 --> 37:54.900
How's the injury?

37:54.901 --> 37:56.141
Let me take a look.

37:56.631 --> 37:58.471
It's all for the future
of the Dou family.

37:59.721 --> 38:02.071
Just a little flesh wound. It's nothing.

38:03.601 --> 38:04.741
Ms. Longevity.

38:05.371 --> 38:07.671
I only just found out about this.

38:08.011 --> 38:09.160
If I were here,

38:09.161 --> 38:11.021
I would never let them hurt you.

38:11.891 --> 38:14.151
Mr. Wu's condition is worse
in the prison.

38:14.561 --> 38:15.941
Father always thinks highly of him.

38:16.491 --> 38:18.021
Why don't you visit him?

38:23.291 --> 38:24.431
It's been over ten years.

38:26.371 --> 38:27.950
I've returned to you once again.

38:27.951 --> 38:29.330
(Perpetual Bloom)

38:29.331 --> 38:31.151
In return, what did I get?

38:32.201 --> 38:35.501
Slaps and foot punishment.

38:39.161 --> 38:40.301
Father.

38:42.081 --> 38:43.591
Will I

38:44.851 --> 38:47.231
be grounded forever?

38:48.121 --> 38:49.381
That's not possible.

38:50.081 --> 38:51.221
It'll be lifted.

38:51.561 --> 38:54.591
It'll be lifted now.

38:58.331 --> 38:59.370
Lord Song.

38:59.371 --> 39:01.541
If you turn yourself in now,
we'll lose everything we've done.

39:01.851 --> 39:03.271
Dezhen is weak.

39:03.281 --> 39:05.741
He won't be able to withstand Shengtian
Prefecture's trap and punishment.

39:05.931 --> 39:07.461
I can't let him suffer for me.

39:07.521 --> 39:08.490
I'll turn myself in.

39:08.491 --> 39:09.901
I have a way to end this.

39:43.041 --> 39:44.120
(It's windy and snowy.)

39:44.121 --> 39:45.261
(What are you doing here?)

39:45.721 --> 39:46.850
(Your legs are severely injured.)

39:46.851 --> 39:48.091
(Do you want to lose your legs?)

39:48.971 --> 39:50.341
You promised me.

39:51.411 --> 39:52.751
If I saved you,

39:53.331 --> 39:54.861
you'll cherish this life

39:55.011 --> 39:56.151
and fight to stay alive.

39:56.971 --> 39:58.231
At this point in time,

39:58.371 --> 40:00.151
there's no way you could save Wu Shan.

40:00.361 --> 40:01.970
Instead, you'll give
those hiding in the dark

40:01.971 --> 40:03.711
a chance to accuse you more.

40:04.771 --> 40:07.231
Your closed ones will be hurt
and your enemies will be laughing.

40:23.291 --> 40:24.490
Let me.

40:24.491 --> 40:25.490
Don't move.

40:25.491 --> 40:26.631
You'll scratch it again.

40:31.561 --> 40:32.791
Didn't you say so?

40:33.601 --> 40:34.810
In the eyes of a physician,

40:34.811 --> 40:36.191
it's just a body.

40:36.201 --> 40:37.341
There's no gender boundary.

40:38.201 --> 40:39.421
Why are you shy?

40:40.411 --> 40:42.240
I injured my legs,

40:42.241 --> 40:43.791
not my hands.

40:44.291 --> 40:45.901
They said it was a foot punishment,

40:45.911 --> 40:47.631
but actually, they were aiming
for something else

40:47.771 --> 40:49.421
so they didn't beat me hard.

40:49.451 --> 40:50.821
My legs will be fine.

40:52.721 --> 40:54.541
How about you?

40:55.331 --> 40:56.471
Let me see.

41:15.291 --> 41:16.431
Why is the Wu family

41:17.401 --> 41:19.021
will be involved in something
between you and me?

41:20.721 --> 41:22.671
When they were punishing me
at the ancestral hall,

41:22.781 --> 41:24.720
Fifth Uncle purposely sent the news
to the Wu family

41:24.721 --> 41:26.311
and made the fake blood garment.

41:27.891 --> 41:29.311
Wu Shan was framed for imprisonment

41:29.561 --> 41:30.941
because of me.

41:31.451 --> 41:33.850
I've sent people to check
what's going on at the Shengtian Prison.

41:33.851 --> 41:36.421
The confession is all about gang up.

41:37.161 --> 41:38.791
I didn't realize so much had happened

41:39.331 --> 41:40.861
in the few days I'd been in bed.

41:42.491 --> 41:44.821
What Fifth Uncle has said enlighten me.

41:44.921 --> 41:46.751
A gentleman planned his time

41:46.761 --> 41:48.371
and acted when the time came.

41:48.561 --> 41:50.191
Going against God's will

41:50.721 --> 41:52.501
is not going to end well.

41:52.891 --> 41:54.541
This case

41:54.561 --> 41:56.090
is not about having an affair.

41:56.091 --> 41:59.151
It's about Li Zhen's rebellion
in Liaodong.

41:59.241 --> 42:01.191
Should we fight or make peace?

42:02.971 --> 42:04.591
What is the situation in Liaodong?

42:04.971 --> 42:08.461
Official Wu and the rest in the Cabinet
advise to start a war.

42:08.811 --> 42:10.450
They even use the ancestral's motto.

42:10.451 --> 42:11.370
We will speak
even if it means death to us.

42:11.371 --> 42:13.631
His Majesty doesn't want to start a war
with Li Zhen.

42:14.041 --> 42:16.901
After all, there's a financial deficit.

42:16.971 --> 42:18.151
The country has no marshals.

42:18.331 --> 42:19.941
His Majesty doesn't want to go to war?

42:21.811 --> 42:23.631
Liaodong has no troops

42:24.051 --> 42:25.900
and no experience in war.

42:25.901 --> 42:28.541
The country is running out of money,
it's difficult to start a long war.

42:28.771 --> 42:31.111
Wu has a loyal heart.
He wanted to fight.

42:31.971 --> 42:33.501
The more he speaks,

42:33.521 --> 42:35.381
the harder for His Majesty
to get out of this.

42:36.371 --> 42:38.271
Fifth Uncle has been
a humble servant for years,

42:39.121 --> 42:41.341
but now he dares to sue the Wu family.

42:41.891 --> 42:43.541
I bet he figured out
His Majesty's intention.

42:45.121 --> 42:46.271
According to you,

42:46.491 --> 42:48.421
Mr. Wu's advice is untimely.

42:48.521 --> 42:49.791
He's not going to make it.

42:50.851 --> 42:51.991
I'm afraid

42:52.521 --> 42:54.231
this will be a tough one.

42:58.851 --> 43:01.501
If they can put aside right and wrong,
honor and disgrace,

43:01.771 --> 43:03.461
we might be able to solve this.

43:06.451 --> 43:10.751
The root cause is between
Old Master Wu and His Majesty.

43:27.601 --> 43:29.850
The most unpredictable thing
in the world

43:29.851 --> 43:31.311
is the human heart.

43:31.591 --> 43:33.160
If I were to do it again,

43:33.161 --> 43:35.711
I'm afraid
I couldn't stay out of it too.

43:36.081 --> 43:37.490
I'd rather die

43:37.491 --> 43:39.981
than admit this false accusation.

43:40.291 --> 43:41.431
Beheaded!

43:42.541 --> 43:47.020
♪I lean in and gaze at you
as calm as serene waves♪

43:47.021 --> 43:50.781
♪I'm aware of the vast
and turbulent world♪

43:50.941 --> 43:55.331
♪Moving forward alone, the expectations
of many are hard to bear♪

43:55.511 --> 43:59.440
♪When the time comes,
I will cast aside a lifetime of pride♪

43:59.441 --> 44:02.420
♪To wear a flower stick for you♪

44:02.421 --> 44:04.630
♪Or perhaps my heart
yearns for the other side♪

44:04.631 --> 44:07.191
♪Yet there's no place for me
to go in the end♪

44:07.241 --> 44:10.811
♪Your presence
by my side is irreplaceable♪

44:10.871 --> 44:14.391
♪Like a ship crossing
the desolate river♪

44:14.401 --> 44:18.380
♪That brings me
through a chapter of my life♪

44:18.381 --> 44:22.411
♪You are the light
that saves me in the darkness♪

44:22.851 --> 44:26.311
♪Having you is a blessing♪

44:26.471 --> 44:28.651
♪My heart filled with warmth♪

44:28.671 --> 44:32.501
♪By your side,
I spend the rest of my life♪

44:32.831 --> 44:35.971
♪Your presence
by my side is irreplaceable♪

44:36.511 --> 44:39.921
♪Where my heart yearns
is where I will go♪

44:40.361 --> 44:43.901
♪Breaking waves over the desolate river♪

44:44.101 --> 44:47.770
♪The wind rises as my heart finds peace♪

44:47.771 --> 44:52.111
♪You are the light
that saves me in the darkness♪

44:52.171 --> 44:55.900
♪Having you is a blessing♪

44:55.901 --> 44:59.380
♪Only by being by your side♪

44:59.381 --> 45:04.061
♪I can spend the rest of my life♪

45:04.091 --> 45:07.680
♪Until the waves are all spread out♪

45:07.681 --> 45:11.821
♪And the past sinks into the river♪

45:11.891 --> 45:15.181
♪Always together, looking back♪

45:15.491 --> 45:22.791
♪Only sighing at the commotion♪

45:32.031 --> 45:33.070
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama)

45:33.071 --> 45:34.030
(Every medical behaviour involved
and medicine used in the drama)

45:34.031 --> 45:35.251
(is required by the story.
Please don't try this at home)
